# Filippo Argenti — an artfully crafted intellect

![essence of Filippo Argenti](filippo-argenti.png)
<!-- carbon badge (8-bit portrait): filippo-argenti.tiff -->

**what —** A wrathful soul in the marsh of the Styx who lunges at the passing boat.

**why —** A rage that could never be governed.

**how —** He is torn at by the other wrathful — and Dante, for once, is glad to watch.

**where —** Circle V — Wrath (Phlegyas ferries; the sullen choke below the mud).

